 <subsection xml:id="subsec-Squares-of-fractions">
        <title>Squares of fractions</title>
        <p>
            We have seen how to find squares of whole numbers <xref ref="subsec-Squares-of-whole-numbers"/>. But what about fractions?
            A fraction contains of a numerator and a denominator, both of which are whole numbers.
            Squaring a fraction follows the same way as squaring whole numbers, in which we simply multiply both the numerator and the denominator by themselves. 
        </p>
